title: Felipe Martins
text:
Felipe Santos Martins (born 12 November 1990) is a Brazilian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who last played for <a href="Song%20Lam%20Nghe%20An%20FC">Song Lam Nghe An</a>.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Segunda%20Liga">Segunda Liga</a> for <a href="C.D.%20Aves">Desportivo Aves</a> on 8 August 2015 in a game against <a href="S.C.%20Covilh%C3%A3">Sporting Covilhã</a>.
